  "texts": [
    "All models were trained on an NVIDIA A100-SXM4-80GPU on a High Performance Cluster.",
    "HistoGPT-L required 7 days of training.",
    "During training, we randomly augmented the text inputs to avoid overfitting common words and phrases.",
    "This was done beforehand using GPT-4 to sample 9 paraphrased reports with the default temperature of 1.0 and nucleus sampling of 1.0.",
    "The prompt used was: \"Rewrite the following text but be as accurate and faithful as possible to the original."
